      "html": "<section class=\"slide eq\"><ul class=\"eq-lines\"><li id=\"imox7gol51i\" class=\" eq-item eq-title \" > Checking the Answer </li><li id=\"imox7gol51j\" class=\" eq-item eq-math \" > $$ x = 4 $$ </li><li id=\"imox7gol51k\" class=\" eq-item eq-math \" > $$ 2(4)+3=11 $$ </li><li id=\"imox7gol51l\" class=\" eq-item eq-math \" > $$ 8+3=11 $$ </li><li id=\"imox7gol51m\" class=\" eq-item eq-math \" > $$ 11=11 $$ </li><li id=\"imox7gol51n\" class=\" eq-item eq-line \" > Verification completes the reasoning. </li></ul><div class=\"eq-side-panel\"><div id=\"imox7gol51i-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" ><img src=\"image.png\" /></div><div id=\"imox7gol51i-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Verification is part of solving. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51j-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Substitute into the original equation. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51j-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Use the discovered value carefully. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51j-sp-3\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > 2x+3=11 </div><div id=\"imox7gol51j-sp-4\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Replace x with 4. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51j-sp-5\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Now evaluate step by step. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51j-sp-6\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Verification catches hidden mistakes. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51k-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" ><img src=\"eq.webp\" /></div><div id=\"imox7gol51k-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Multiply before adding. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51l-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > The arithmetic is now simple. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51l-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > 8+3 </div><div id=\"imox7gol51l-sp-3\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Both sides match correctly. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51l-sp-4\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > The equality remains true. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51l-sp-5\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > The solution is confirmed. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51l-sp-6\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > No contradiction appears. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51m-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" ><img src=\"box.webp\" /></div><div id=\"imox7gol51m-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Both sides are identical. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51n-sp-1\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Correct answers should survive checking. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51n-sp-2\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > This strengthens mathematical confidence. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51n-sp-3\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Students learn disciplined solving. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51n-sp-4\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Every equation deserves verification. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51n-sp-5\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Careful checking prevents careless mistakes. </div><div id=\"imox7gol51n-sp-6\" class=\"eq-explain-item hidden\" > Reasoning becomes trustworthy. </div></div></section>",
